    "section": "Contact Me",
    "text": "Contact Me\nPlease feel free to contact me via email. However, to ensure fairness and consistency for all students, I will not respond to three categories of inquiries:\n\nQuestions regarding information that is already available on the website\nRequests for make-up examination, presentations, or attendance adjustments\nRequests for special arrangements regarding examination or presentation schedules\n\nThank you for your understanding as we work to keep our learning environment fair for everyone."
